          "title": "DGB p2p connection disconnects every 60 seconds, no block updates received",
          "body": "A disconnect happens between NOMP and the digibyted p2p port after exactly 60 seconds. No block updates are ever received via this method from digibyted. RPC polls and blockupdate methods both work fine. The peermagic supplied in the coin configs is correct. Connections are successfully made, and a peer shows up as connected using the digibyted api, but then a disconnect happens after 60 seconds every time. NOMP reconnects, and then another disconnect after 60 seconds. Repeat.\r\n\r\nCould something cause this on the digibyted side? \r\nsome logs:\r\n\r\n\r\n--- nomp ----\r\n2018-08-04 18:52:23 [Pool]      [digibyte-qubit] (Thread 2) p2p connection successful\r\n2018-08-04 18:52:50 [Pool]      [digibyte-qubit] (Thread 1) Block notification via RPC polling\r\n2018-08-04 18:52:50 [Pool]      [digibyte-qubit] (Thread 2) Block notification via RPC polling\r\n2018-08-04 18:53:01 [Pool]      [digibyte-qubit] (Thread 1) Block notification via RPC polling\r\n2018-08-04 18:53:01 [Pool]      [digibyte-qubit] (Thread 2) Block notification via RPC polling\r\n2018-08-04 18:53:06 [Pool]      [digibyte-qubit] (Thread 2) Block notification via RPC polling\r\n2018-08-04 18:53:06 [Pool]      [digibyte-qubit] (Thread 1) Block notification via RPC polling\r\n2018-08-04 18:53:20 [Pool]      [digibyte-qubit] (Thread 2) Block notification via RPC polling\r\n2018-08-04 18:53:20 [Pool]      [digibyte-qubit] (Thread 1) Block notification via RPC polling\r\n2018-08-04 18:53:24 [Pool]      [digibyte-qubit] (Thread 2) p2p peer node disconnected - attempting reconnection...\r\n2018-08-04 18:53:24 [Pool]      [digibyte-qubit] (Thread 1) p2p peer node disconnected - attempting reconnection...\r\n2018-08-04 18:53:24 [Pool]      [digibyte-qubit] (Thread 2) p2p connection successful\r\n2018-08-04 18:53:24 [Pool]      [digibyte-qubit] (Thread 1) p2p connection successful\r\n\r\n---digibyte getpeerinfo---\r\n {\r\n    \"id\": 56,\r\n    \"addr\": \"127.0.0.1:53512\",\r\n    \"addrbind\": \"127.0.0.1:12024\",\r\n    \"services\": \"0000000000000001\",\r\n    \"relaytxes\": true,\r\n    \"lastsend\": 1533408926,\r\n    \"lastrecv\": 1533408926,\r\n    \"bytessent\": 151,\r\n    \"bytesrecv\": 123,\r\n    \"conntime\": 1533408926,\r\n    \"timeoffset\": 0,\r\n    \"version\": 70016,\r\n    \"subver\": \"/node-stratum/\",\r\n    \"inbound\": true,\r\n    \"addnode\": false,\r\n    \"startingheight\": 0,\r\n    \"banscore\": 0,\r\n    \"synced_headers\": -1,\r\n    \"synced_blocks\": -1,\r\n    \"inflight\": [\r\n    ],\r\n    \"whitelisted\": false,\r\n    \"bytessent_per_msg\": {\r\n      \"verack\": 24,\r\n      \"version\": 127\r\n    },\r\n    \"bytesrecv_per_msg\": {\r\n      \"version\": 123\r\n    }\r\n  },",
